We can now compute the percentage of the flotation cost which is computed as follows: 
$$\begin{aligned}
\text{Flotation cost percentage}&=\dfrac{\text{Total cost}}{\text{Stock offering, net amount}}\\[10pt]
&=\dfrac{\text{\$132,670,000.00}}{\text{\$426,530,000.00}}\\[10pt]
&={\textbf{31.10\%}}
\end{aligned}$$
